'''2016年奇洛埃地震'''為發生於[[智利|智利]]南部[[蒙特港|蒙特港]]西南方225公里，地震規模為7.7，是次地震引發海嘯，因此對震央周圍1,000公里地區發布海嘯警報<ref name=USGS25Dec16>{{cite web|url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/us10007mn3|title=M7.6 – 39km SSW of Puerto Quellón, Chile|publisher=[[United_States_Geological_Survey|United States Geological Survey]]|accessdate=December 25, 2016|archive-date=2016-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161226013505/http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/us10007mn3|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="usgs"/><ref name="bbc">{{cite news |title=Chile earthquake triggers tsunami warning |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-38430564 |work=BBC |date=25 December 2016 |accessdate=25 December 2016 |archive-date=2016-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161226084945/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-38430564 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[奇洛埃岛|奇洛埃岛]]居民據智利政府指示，進行大規模撤離<ref name="bbc"/>。島上部分地區出現些許受損，但無人員傷亡。

